---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About CalcForDIY — Free Home Improvement Calculators"
  description="CalcForDIY provides free, accurate calculators for home improvement and DIY projects."
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">About CalcForDIY</h1>

  <div class="prose max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-4">
    <p>
      CalcForDIY is a free collection of calculators built for homeowners, 
      DIY enthusiasts, and contractors who need fast, accurate estimates for 
      home improvement projects.
    </p>
    <p>
      Every calculator on this site runs entirely in your browser. Nothing is 
      uploaded to a server. No account required. No hidden fees.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our calculators cover tile, flooring, paint, lighting, concrete, and more — 
      with new tools added regularly. Each one is built around verified industry 
      formulas from sources like the Tile Council of North America and the 
      National Wood Flooring Association.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you find an error or want to suggest a calculator, use the contact 
      information below.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Contact: hello@calcfordiy.com</p>
  </div>
</Layout>